{"type":null,"faqId":48066,"title":"数据与同步","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“华为云服务”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>在“数据与同步”区域，您可以：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“联系人”，然后点击“自动同步”开关。开启后，云端的联系人将与您的手机保持同步。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>点击“信息”、“通话记录”、“备忘录”、“录音”或“云相册”开关，开启后，相关数据将被自动上传到云端。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178053\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>您可以设置仅在 WLAN 网络下上传备忘录、录音、相机照片和视频等文件。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1070,"faqType":"华为云应用","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3652","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hicloud","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598108000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":135,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType